{{flavour|Spits a glob of sticky flame at an adjacent creature, covering it in liquid fire for a short time. It may also splash onto other nearby creatures on impact.}}

'''Sticky Flame Splash''' is the monster spell equivalent to the player mottled [[draconian]]'s [[draconian breath attacks|breath weapon]]. It was only found on monstrous [[mottled draconian]]s of all varieties (including [[Tiamat]], if she was mottled).

==History==
Sticky Flame Splash was removed in [[0.20]].

